sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as NguoiDung
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant AiSvc as AiTaskService
participant TaskSvc as TaskService
participant AiDb as Mongo_AiTaskExtraction

Note over User,AiDb: Chặng 2 - Confirm tạo task thật + lỗi
User->>Client: Xác nhận tạo task
Client->>AiSvc: POST /api/ai-tasks/confirm + Idempotency-Key
AiSvc->>TaskSvc: Tạo task thật
alt Thành công
  AiSvc->>AiDb: Mark confirmed
  AiSvc-->>Client: 201 created
else Trùng idempotency
  AiSvc-->>Client: 409 conflict
else Task service lỗi
  AiSvc-->>Client: 5xx
end
